{"analytics_identifier":"OT1429","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-digital-identities-and-attributes","content_id":"aa1dfc50-e5b8-47d1-b068-27b98d318550","description":"The Office for Digital Identities and Attributes enables the use of trusted digital identity services in the UK. OfDIA is part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology .","details":{"acronym":"OfDIA","alternative_format_contact_email":"alt.formats@dsit.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Office for Digital Identities and Attributes enables the use of trusted digital identity services in the UK.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office for Digital Identities and Attributes\">OfDIA</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-science-innovation-and-technology\">Department for Science, Innovation and Technology</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-science-innovation-technology","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/671ba3021037a76fc9903e46/s960_office-for-digital-identities-dsit-style.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/671ba302956d9b52e8c6d2a6/s300_office-for-digital-identities-dsit-style.jpg"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office for Digital<br/>Identities &amp; Attributes"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/new-data-laws-will-make-life-easier-for-british-people-cutting-life-admin-easing-traffic-and-speeding-up-roadworks","image":{"alt_text":"A person holds a smartphone. The image has blue and red triangular borders.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e517461d68e6ee1a92adb/s712_DataBillimage.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5174f85b4b993fd7531e/s465_DataBillimage.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e517461d68e6ee1a92ada/DataBillimage.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-06-19T13:34:26.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>British people will benefit from new laws which will make their day-to-day lives easier – from slashing grocery bills and cutting traffic jams to speeding up NHS diagnoses – as the government delivers on manifesto commitments.</p>\n</div>","title":"New data laws will make life easier for British people, cutting life admin, easing traffic and speeding up roadworks"},{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://enablingdigitalidentity.blog.gov.uk/2025/06/26/sharing-the-final-gamma-0-4-trust-framework-and-updated-supplementary-codes/","image":{"alt_text":"A woman holds a smartphone. The image has a red and white border.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5241c2633bd820a92aec/s712_TFimage.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5241e44db4975be00b0b/s465_TFimage.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5241f85b4b993fd75321/TFimage.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-06-26T00:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The final publication of the ‘gamma’ (0.4) UK digital identity and attributes trust framework is now live on GOV.UK.</p>\n</div>","title":"Sharing the final gamma (0.4) trust framework and updated supplementary codes"},{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://enablingdigitalidentity.blog.gov.uk/2025/05/30/digital-identity-and-the-gov-uk-wallet-increasing-choice-accelerating-adoption/","image":{"alt_text":"Secretary of State for Science, Innovation and Technology, Peter Kyle. The image has a red and white border on the left hand side.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5bc261d68e6ee1a92aea/s712_PeterKyleimage.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/685e5bc262b2e559cbd75328/s465_PeterKyleimage.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.servi